<item>
            <title>[LU-15102] Reset lnet_ni::ni_ping_count when rx is finalized, not tx</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15102</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The lnet_ni:ni_ping_count is currently reset on every (healthy) tx. We should only reset it when receiving a message over the NI. Taking net_lock 0 on every tx results in a performance loss for certain workloads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="66633">LU-15102</key>
